thread.title: Elon Musk brings technology charm offensive to high tech tunnel plan

title: Elon Musk brings technology charm offensive to high tech tunnel plan
text:
Elon Musk brings technology charm offensive to high tech tunnel plan Friday, May 18, 2018 - 01:37
Billionaire entrepreneur Elon Musk is bringing his technology charm offensive to an attempt at digging a tunnel beneath part of Los Angeles to test designs for a high-speed subterranean transportation network he envisions for the city. Ryan Brooks reports
